“Cinema is a matter of what’s in the frame and what’s out” 
Martin Scorsese
.
It seems easy and logical but it’s not.!
It’s a matter of feeling and sensitivity. It’s about what you want to tell, what you want your audience think or believe 
¡It’s art.!
